a sample 1-2 minute video using a buzzfeed post a inspiration send u an unlisted link and mention the title of the buzzfeed post you based it on focus on clarity and engagement inform u entertain u inspire u make u want to share it
links to your own published video that showcase your unique voice connect with internet sharer and are consistent with what you'd like to do at buzzfeed
